mai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1367710/extras/7e5f7682452f5c48b6aa97f402417ab7.poster.avif?t=1769669945\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1367710/extras/7e5f7682452f5c48b6aa97f402417ab7.webm?t=1769669945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1367710/extras/7e5f7682452f5c48b6aa97f402417ab7.mp4?t=1769669945\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>史诗级Boss战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对<strong>更强大、更致命的Boss</strong>，他们将<strong>随剧情推进不断进化</strong>！<strong>每场战斗都是对你战斗技巧与策略的终极考验！</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>电影级爆炸战斗，肾上腺素狂飙！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>快节奏激战+电影级视觉冲击</strong>，让你沉浸在疯狂战斗之中！迎战<strong>嗜血吸血鬼及他们的统治者</strong>，感受纯正硬核射击快感！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多样化场景，自由探索！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿梭于<strong>巨型工业基地、火星采矿场、奢华摩天大楼</strong>，探索<strong>充满神秘气息的邪教研究设施</strong>，解开隐藏的黑暗秘密。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>你的选择决定命运！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为<strong>特种部队精英 罗恩·亚当斯</strong>，你将建立<strong>盟友、迎战强敌</strong>，并决定<strong>身边所有人的命运</strong>。你的每个选择都会塑造你的未来—<strong>你会保持人性，还是堕入黑暗？</strong></p>",
